txt.en: 'I am glad to see your face again, [placeholder], and to see that you continue to do good work. Thank you for these supplies.'
'If you plan to travel west to Ost Lontir, could you bring this crate to Gilanor? The townspeople have been waiting for these supplies.\n\n'He'll be sure to pay you for your work.'
Bruidis has asked you to deliver supplies to the people of Ost Lontir.
Gilanor can be found in Ost Lontir, to the west of Tadrent.\n\nYou should deliver these supplies to him.
Talk to Gilanor in Ost Lontir
